            "title": "The Enigmatic Spelaeorhynchidae Oudemans, 1902 (Acari:Mesostigmata) Blood-Feeding Ectoparasites Infesting NeotropicalBats, with Catalog and Notes on a Collection from the ManúBiosphere Reserve in Peru",
            "creators": [
